Nov 6 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Thursday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

CASEY, QUIRK & ASSOCIATES LLC  The management consulting firm named Peter Chambers as a senior adviser for Europe. [ID:nL4N0SW7QB]  BNY MELLON CORP <BK.N>  The bank appointed Marcelino Pendas as a senior director and team leader in the company's international wealth management group's Miami office. [ID:nL4N0SW7RE]  SANDITON ASSET MANAGEMENT  London-based asset management firm said it appointed Guy Hill senior investment director. [ID:nL4N0SW7R6]  RATHBONE INVESTMENT MANAGEMENT  The UK-based investment management firm appointed Will Roberts as an investment director in its Liverpool office. [ID:nL4N0SW7PT]  MORGAN STANLEY <MS.N> The financial services company's investment management unit has named Jens Nystedt as managing director at its emerging markets debt team. [ID:nL4N0SW7HU]  PINEBRIDGE INVESTMENTS  The asset manager said it named John Thornton as non-executive chairman, effective Nov. 21. [ID:nL4N0SW7JP]  BEAZLEY PLC <BEZG.L>